## DATA FETCHING — PADRÕES CORRETOS

### Parallel Fetching (performance)
```typescript
// ✅ Busca paralela — não sequencial!
export default async function StudentDashboard() {
  const [profile, trainings, xpLog] = await Promise.all([
    getProfile(),
    getTrainings(),
    getXPLog(),
  ]);
  
  return <Dashboard profile={profile} trainings={trainings} xp={xpLog} />;
}
```

### Suspense para streaming
```tsx
import { Suspense } from 'react';
import { TrainingSkeleton } from '@/components/skeletons';

export default function Page() {
  return (
    <Suspense fallback={<TrainingSkeleton />}>
      <TrainingList />  {/* async Server Component */}
    </Suspense>
  );
}
```

